{"tid":920680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無人機結合奧迪汽車首飛　10年內可搭到「飛天車」","createTime":"2018-11-29T03:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T04:13:48.000Z","uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"098c05575a5f3b5c9fd40aa13272fbef2b185b62","tid":920680,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:56:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zO114BNxmvc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzO114BNxmvc&d=U0Pt4ZSIax%2BM6%2FJa6Mfzr9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a9298ce4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zO114BNxmvc</a><br />\n一輛飛行汽車比例模型「Pop.Up Next」27日在荷蘭阿姆斯特丹的展覽上首飛，由航太公司空中巴士（Airbus）、汽車製造商奧迪（Audi）和義大利設計公司Italdesign共同研發，比例為原計劃大小的四分之一。這樣的概念主要是讓乘客能夠乘坐四輪汽車，同時也能在空中飛行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3726/d3726157.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3726%2Fd3726157.jpg&h=b53bc029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無人機飛行車Pop.Up Next在阿姆斯特丹展示。<br />\n綜合外媒報導，這輛名為「Pop.Up Next」的飛行汽車模型27日在阿姆斯特丹的無人機週（Amsterdam Drone Week）上試飛，主要由3個元件組成，包括雙人座車艙、輪子的底架以及四旋翼無人機。<br />\n在試飛過程中，一架四旋翼無人機降落在舞台，接著一輛奧迪的模型車載著雙人座車艙在下方行駛，隨後車艙被扣在無人機的底部，接著起飛離開。無人機扣著車艙飛行一段時間後，再次停下回到原點，等待奧迪模型車底架行駛過來，兩者對準後，無人機底盤的車艙再次接回模型車上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3726/d3726158.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3726%2Fd3726158.jpg&h=6c1bd285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奧迪模型車載著乘客艙，等待無人機過來銜接。<br />\n據報導，由於越來越多人搬到城市，交通阻塞一直是很大的問題，因此3間公司合作研發這項產品，希望未來能正式上市，供民眾搭乘。設計公司Italdesign總裁馬滕斯（Bernd Martens）表示，飛行出租車再通過一些步驟即可上路。<br />\n奧迪董事會成員表示，目前還不清楚這輛飛行車「Pop.Up Next」要如何迅速轉變為商業產品，但相信在未來10年內能發生。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2LggHhR2kFk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2LggHhR2kFk&d=U0Pt4ZSIax%2BM6%2FJa6Mfzr9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=f85933ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2LggHhR2kFk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181129/1317905.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181129%2F1317905.htm&d=U0Pt4ZSIax%2BM6%2FJa6Mfzr9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=7fc9fcec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181129/1317905.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/47/1d/ad/471dadaae7bfc1f960305d476a824f49.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F47%2F1d%2Fad%2F471dadaae7bfc1f960305d476a824f49.gif&h=6d100c83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://3oneseven.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/spinner-police.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3oneseven.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fspinner-police.gif&h=7469773e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64be093a05334e36f5772eea307ea7da8854577","tid":920680,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b658f1de315b3846f50a48f64362da0aed6d76c","tid":920680,"uid":136386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:13:48.000Z","msg":"We are in the future now"}]}